MISCELLANEOUS DOCKET

92-1967. In re Gregersen.

Pursuant to the provisions of Gov. Bar R. I(8)(H), Craig Gregersen, Attorney Registration No. 0040034, is permitted to register for inactive status.

Moyer, C.J., Wright and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., dissent and would revoke his license pursuant to Gov. Bar R. I(8)(H).
